      <h3>Location</h3>
      <p>Neighborhood hub with pickup, delivery, and a cozy corner for quick bites.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="about-card">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>Phone: (555) 010-PEP</p>
      <p>Email: pie@cowabungapizza.test</p>
